{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"206c880fe4","title":"对大跃进报导的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d9986acc2d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"206c880fe4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958.1-1960）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a55756f7fd","type":"paragraph","text":"对大跃进报导的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"cc200ec815","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年末于武昌）","index":1,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"1746057619","type":"paragraph","text":"要实事求是，不要浮夸，要作冷静的促进派，要鼓实劲，不要鼓虚劲，冲天的干劲要与严格的科学的态度相结合。","index":2,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"e85d36d0cb","type":"paragraph","text":"对地方党委导新间事业的指示","index":3,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"b2d6fa0dbc","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年）","index":4,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"c2deb20b65","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年，新华社国内分社和人民日报记者站合并，体制下放给地方党委，会向主席汇报此事，主席说。","index":5,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"a369918bde","type":"paragraph","text":"早就应该这样做，过去（分社）省也管不了，现在这个办法是适应国家的情况的。省委管比你们有办法，分社也就不孤单了，就有依靠了。","index":6,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"a179b86d9c","type":"paragraph","text":"关于造船方斜的指示","index":7,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"1a20c84419","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年月）","index":8,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"},{"id":"9ff5973eed","type":"paragraph","text":"在我国现代工业、现代农业、现代科学文化发展的基础上，国防力量的建设不仅要作好积极防御的准备工作，同时还要准备一且帝国主义向我国发动侵略战争时，在打败敌人之后，实施战略反攻和战略追击，把侵略者赶同他们的本土，坚决、干净、彻底全部消灭之，解放那里的人民，以便侵略战争永远不再发生。为此，除了继续加强陆军和室军建设以外，必须大搞造船工业，建立海上铁路，以便在今后若干年内建设一支强大的海上战斗力量。","index":9,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4"}],"page":{"id":"1b7c8c10fa","publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"206c880fe4","start":199,"end":199}}}},"__N_SSG":true}